snippet.title: Olliefrog Toad Skater - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX x Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Get a fresh look at Olliefrog Toad Skater to see sick tricks performed by adorable froggy friends and gameplay from this upcoming skateboarding game where it's easy to be steezy. In Olliefrog Toad Skater, create and customize your own cute little frog an tear up one of the skateparks in this fast responsive combo-driven score and objective-based skateboarding title which stays faithful to the arcade action skating games of the late 90s/early 2000s. Olliefrog Toad Skater is coming to PC in 2024.
